{
  "texts": [
    "Moreover, exploring the integration of these models with other spam detection techniques, such as behavioral analysis and anomaly detection, could offer holistic approaches to spam mitigation.",
    "Finally, assessing the models' performance in dynamic environments, where spam tactics continually evolve, would provide deeper insights into their long-term effectiveness and adaptability.",
    "This study embarked on a comparative analysis of two advanced artificial intelligence models, ChatGPT-4 by OpenAI and Google Gemini, to evaluate their efficacy in identifying spam within the SpamAssassin public mail corpus.",
    "The results revealed that both models demonstrate significant strengths in spam detection, yet they exhibit distinct characteristics in their performance metrics.",
    "ChatGPT-4 showed a balanced performance with high accuracy, precision, recall, and F1-score, indicating its robust capability to distinguish between spam and legitimate emails effectively."
  ]
}